    <h3 class="font-weight-bold">3: Phalanx</h3>
    <p style=" text-align:left">Phalanx is also such a cool design too and he flies through the air like avion. What makes him different is his sheer size as he's almost 
        the biggest in the game and his sacks that theoretically aid him in flight. This is thought to be true since you have to shoot them with arrows as you ride your horse
        to get him to a low enough altitude to climb. Once he's low enough you can climb his wings and go for the three weakpoints. What I also like about this fight is the amazing music that plays
        when you manage to get on top of him. It's also unique to Phalanx's fight and it's wonderful. However, he gets the thrid spot because sometimes it can be a real challenge hitting the sacks
        and you have to hit all of them three times as Phalanx likes to hide from you underground after he knocks you off two times. This can make the fight a little long so 3 seems appropriate.</p>

